quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  2,106,MA NENSEH MIN ‘AJETIN ‘EW NUNSIHA NE’TI BIHAJRIN MINHA ‘EW MITHLIHA ‘ELEM TA’LEM ‘ENNEL-LAHE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  2,107,‘ELEM TA’LEM ‘ENNEL-LAHE LEHU MULKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA LEKUM MIN DUNI ELLAHI MIN WE LIJIN WE LA NESIRIN
  2,108,‘EM TURIDUNE ‘EN TES’ELU RESULEKUM KEMA SU’ILE MUSA MIN KABLU WE MEN JETEBEDDELIL-KUFRE BIL-’IMANI FEKAD DELLE SEWA’E ES-SEBILI
  2,109,WEDDE KETHIRUN MIN ‘EHLIL-KITABI LEW JERUDDUNEKUM MIN BA’DI ‘IMANIKUM KUFFARÆN HESEDÆN MIN ‘INDI ‘ENFUSIHIM MIN BA’DI MA TEBEJJENE LEHUMUL-HEKKU FA’FU WE ESFEHU HETTA JE’TIJEL-LAHU BI’EMRIHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  2,110,WE ‘EKIMU ES-SELÆTE WE ‘ATU EZ-ZEKÆTE WE MA TUKADDIMU LI’NFUSIKUM MIN HAJRIN TEXHIDUHU ‘INDEL-LAHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE BIMA TA’MELUNE BESIRUN
  2,111,WE KALU LEN JEDHULEL-XHENNETE ‘ILLA MEN KANE HUDÆN ‘EW NESARA TILKE ‘EMANIJUHUM KUL HATU BURHANEKUM ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKIN
  2,112,BELA MEN ‘ESLEME WEXHHEHU LILLAHI WE HUWE MUHSINUN FELEHU ‘EXHRUHU ‘INDE RABBIHI WE LA HAWFUN ‘ALEJHIM WE LA HUM JEHZENUNE
  2,113,WE KALETIL-JEHUDU LEJSETI EN-NESARA ‘ALA SHEJ’IN WE KALETI EN-NESARA LEJSETIL-JEHUDU ‘ALA SHEJ’IN WE HUM JETLUNEL-KITABE KEDHALIKE KALEL-LEDHINE LA JA’LEMUNE MITHLE KAWLIHIM FE-ELLAHU JEHKUMU BEJNEHUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI FIMA KANU FIHI JEHTELIFUNE
  2,114,WE MEN ‘EDHLEMU MIMMEN MENE’A MESAXHIDEL-LAHI ‘EN JUDHKERE FIHA ESMUHU WE SA’A FI HARABIHA ‘ULA’IKE MA KANE LEHUM ‘EN JEDHULUHA ‘ILA HA’IFINE LEHUM FI ED-DUNJA HIZJUN WE LEHUM FIL-’AHIRETI ‘ADHABUN ‘ADHIMUN
  2,115,WE LILLEHIL-MESHRIKU WEL-MEGRIBU FE’EJNEMA TUWELLU FETHEMME WEXHHU ELLAHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE WASI’UN ‘ALIMUN
  2,116,WE KALU ETTEHADHEL-LAHU WELEDÆN SUBHANEHU BEL LEHU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI KULLUN LEHU KANITUNE
  2,117,BEDI’U ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE ‘IDHA KADA ‘EMRÆN FE’INNEMA JEKULU LEHU KUN FEJEKUNU
  2,118,WE KALEL-LEDHINE LA JA’LEMUNE LEWLA JUKELLIMUNALLAHU ‘EW TE’TINA ‘AJETUN KEDHALIKE KALEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM MITHLE KAWLIHIM TESHABEHET KULUBUHUM KAD BEJJENNAL-’AJATI LIKAWMIN JUKINUNE
  2,119,‘INNA ‘ERSELNAKE BIL-HEKKI BESHIRÆN WE NEDHIRÆN WE LA TUS’ELU ‘AN ‘ESHABIL-XHEHIMI
  2,120,WE LEN TERDA ‘ANKEL-JEHUDU WE LA EN-NESARA HETTA TETTEBI’A MILLETEHUM KUL ‘INNE HUDA ELLAHI HUWEL-HUDA WE LE’INI ETTEBA’TE ‘EHWA’EHUM BA’DEL-LEDHI XHA’EKE MINEL-’ILMI MA LEKE MINEL-LAHI MIN WE LIJIN WE LA NESIRIN
  2,121,EL-LEDHINE ‘ATEJNAHUMUL-KITABE JETLUNEHU HEKKA TILAWETIHI ‘ULA’IKE JU’UMINUNE BIHI WE MEN JEKFUR BIHI FE’ULA’IKE HUMUL-HASIRUNE
  2,122,JA BENI ‘ISRA’ILE EDHKURU NI’METIJEL-LETI ‘EN’AMTU ‘ALEJKUM WE ‘ENNI FEDDELTUKUM ‘ALEL-’ALEMINE
  2,123,WE ETTEKU JEWMÆN LA TEXHZI NEFSUN ‘AN NEFSIN SHEJ’ÆN WE LA JUKBELU MINHA ‘ADLUN WE LA TENFA’UHA SHEFA’ATUN WE LA HUM JUNSERUNE